</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/fiction/things-disappear-excerpt-jung-yong-jun">Things That Disappear (<em>an excerpt</em>)</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/jung-yong-jun" hreflang="en">Jung Yong-jun</a>
</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/fiction/wlt-student-translation-prize-prose-marina-and-sergey-dyachenko" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/DyachenkoWolf-a.jpg?itok=hnWWYr4A" width="250" height="175" alt="A detail of the image below focusing on the wolf&#039;s eyes" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/fiction/wlt-student-translation-prize-prose-marina-and-sergey-dyachenko"><em>WLT</em> Student Translation Prize – Prose</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/marina-and-sergey-dyachenko" hreflang="en">Marina and Sergey Dyachenko</a>
</span></div>
        </li>
          </ul>
  </div>
      <a data-jcarousel-control="true" data-target="-=3" class="jcarousel-control-prev"  href="#"></a>
    <a data-jcarousel-control="true" data-target="+=3" class="jcarousel-control-next" href="#"></a>
